SET NOCOUNT ON;
DECLARE @inserted0 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [Audit] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, 0),
(@p8, @p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, @p15, 1),
(@p16, @p17, @p18, @p19, @p20, @p21, @p22, @p23, 2)) AS i ([AffectedColumns], [DateTime], [NewValues], [OldValues], [PrimaryKey], [TableName], [Type], [UserId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AffectedColumns], [DateTime], [NewValues], [OldValues], [PrimaryKey], [TableName], [Type], [UserId])
VALUES (i.[AffectedColumns], i.[DateTime], i.[NewValues], i.[OldValues], i.[PrimaryKey], i.[TableName], i.[Type], i.[UserId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [Audit] t
INNER JOIN @inserted0 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

INSERT INTO [Client] ([Id], [AddedById], [BirthDate], [ClientNumber], [ClientTypeId], [CountryId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [FirstName], [GenderId], [IdDocumentTypeId], [IdNumber], [LastName], [MaritalStatusId], [MiddleName], [ModifiedById], [OccupationId], [Phone], [TitleId])
VALUES (@p24, @p25, @p26, @p27, @p28, @p29, @p30, @p31, @p32, @p33, @p34, @p35, @p36, @p37, @p38, @p39, @p40, @p41, @p42);
DECLARE @inserted4 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [Client] USING (
VALUES (@p43, @p44, @p45, @p46, @p47, @p48, @p49, @p50, @p51, @p52, @p53, @p54, @p55, @p56, @p57, @p58, @p59, @p60, 0)) AS i ([AddedById], [BirthDate], [ClientNumber], [ClientTypeId], [CountryId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [FirstName], [GenderId], [IdDocumentTypeId], [IdNumber], [LastName], [MaritalStatusId], [MiddleName], [ModifiedById], [OccupationId], [Phone], [TitleId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AddedById], [BirthDate], [ClientNumber], [ClientTypeId], [CountryId], [DateAdded], [DateModified], [FirstName], [GenderId], [IdDocumentTypeId], [IdNumber], [LastName], [MaritalStatusId], [MiddleName], [ModifiedById], [OccupationId], [Phone], [TitleId])
VALUES (i.[AddedById], i.[BirthDate], i.[ClientNumber], i.[ClientTypeId], i.[CountryId], i.[DateAdded], i.[DateModified], i.[FirstName], i.[GenderId], i.[IdDocumentTypeId], i.[IdNumber], i.[LastName], i.[MaritalStatusId], i.[MiddleName], i.[ModifiedById], i.[OccupationId], i.[Phone], i.[TitleId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted4;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [Client] t
INNER JOIN @inserted4 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];
